---
<p>1.&nbsp;Go to GoBusiness Licensing Portal website at&nbsp;<a href="https://www.gobusiness.gov.sg/licences">https://www.gobusiness.gov.sg/licences</a>.
</p>
<p>2. Under Search by &quot;Keywords&quot;,&nbsp;
  <br />
  (i) Type in the word &quot;rice&quot; and&nbsp;
  <br />
  (ii) Click &quot;Search&quot;.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>&nbsp;
</p>
<p>3. Under the &quot;Rice Licence&quot; in the Search Results, click &quot;Add to Selection&quot;.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>4. Click &quot;Review &amp; Apply (1)&quot;
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>5. Click &quot;Proceed&quot;.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>6. Click &quot;Apply&quot;.
</p>
<p>&nbsp;
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>&nbsp;
</p>
<p>7. Choose your preferred login method and log in.
</p>
<p><img alt="" height="250" src="https://rice.enterprisesg.gov.sg/portals/0/goBusinessLogin.PNG" width="450" />
</p>
<p>8.&nbsp;(i)&nbsp;Read the Terms of Use.
  <br />
  (ii) Click the &quot;checkbox&quot;.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>9. Select the appropriate radio button.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>10. Check and fill in the Applicant&#39;s particulars.
</p>
<p>&nbsp;<img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>11. Check and fill in the Applicant&#39;s Address.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>&nbsp;
</p>
<p>12. Check and fill in the Organisation Details.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>13. Check and fill in the Organisation Registered Address.&nbsp;
</p>
<p>&nbsp;<img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />&nbsp;
</p>
<p>&nbsp;
</p>
<p>14. Fill in the Organisation Operating Address.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>15. Fill in the Organisation Contact Details.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>16. Fill in the Mailing Address and click &quot;Next&quot;.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>17. Read the licencing conditions and click on the &quot;checkbox&quot; if you agree to the conditions.
</p>
<p>&nbsp;<img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>18. Under the Licence Selection,
  <br />
  (i) Read information of the various types of licence&nbsp;
  <br />
  (ii) Under &quot;Select Only One&quot;, click on the licence you would like to apply.
  <br />
  (ii) Under Type of Rice, select or fill in the appropriate information if needed.
</p>
<p>&nbsp;
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>19. Answer the questions.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>20. Click/ indicate the countries.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>&nbsp;
</p>
<p>21. Fill in your supplier details if applicable.&nbsp;
  <br />
  If you have more than 1 supplier, click &quot;Add&quot; to insert more details.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>22.&nbsp;(i) Select whether you sell rice to wholesalers.
  <br />
  If yes,&nbsp;
  <br />
  (a) Fill in the wholesaler&#39;s details.
  <br />
  (b) Fill in the brand details.
  <br />
  If you have more than 1 brand / supplier, click &quot;Add&quot; to insert more details.&nbsp;
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>23. Fill in your warehousing details.
  <br />
  If you have more than 1 warehouse, click &quot;Add&quot; to insert more details.&nbsp;
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>24.&nbsp;(i) Fill in your business details.
  <br />
  (ii) Check through the details in your form.
  <br />
  (iii) Click &quot;Proceed&quot;.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>25. Read the information and click &quot;Confirm&quot; to proceed with the application.
</p>
<p>&nbsp;<img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />&nbsp;
</p>
<p>26.&nbsp;(i) Do you have any supporting document to provide to us online?
  <br />
  If no, change to select &quot;Offline submission&quot;.
  <br />
  If yes, please click &quot;Upload&quot; to select your file.
  <br />
  (ii) Click &quot;Next&quot; to proceed.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>27.&nbsp;(i) Review your application details.
  <br />
  (ii) Read the General Declarations and click on the &quot;checkbox&quot; if you agree.
  <br />
  (iii) Click &quot;Submit&quot; to proceed.
</p>
<p>&nbsp;<img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>&nbsp;
</p>
<p>28.&nbsp;(i) Review the payment details.
  <br />
  (ii) Click &quot;Proceed with Payment&quot;.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
<p>29.&nbsp;(i) After payment is made, you can click &quot;View Receipt&quot; or &quot;Print&quot; the receipt.&nbsp;
  <br />
  (ii) Click &quot;Close&quot; to end the session.
</p>
<p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," />
</p>
